{"type": "article", "id": 8864, "title": "“Alfi” 椅子系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-24T07:27:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 4, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235215jgfc2Y4NnEOhkeWA.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t英国设计师 Jasper Morrison 最近为 Emeco 推出了一个叫做 “Alfi” 椅子系列，包括一把椅子，两款不同高度的柜子和吧台凳，以及一个三个联排的长椅。椅子全部使用工业废料制成，设计上简约低调，舒适性强，Jasper Morrison 为他们选择了棕色，绿色，深灰色等不同的泥土色彩，视觉选择丰富，对于咖啡厅，酒馆，学校，家庭等都是不错的选择。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235213n6AGCayVkf781LQm.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.58557457\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235213s3ZlTitcDr9d78e6.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.64669927\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235214j5aJy4cnleqOk7HV.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.60757946\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235214QNk9MXoVl5daScj7.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.84841076\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235214oKwTqWgkm5N9ZJ3I.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.55256724\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235215vR3QuBSOVbDTUNm5.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66381418\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}